name: remixing invisible dots inside a fine coconut
description: pls fact... do you hear it ? I hear the leaves of the trees outside my window hustling to the winds blowing in all directions. they sound like a giant crowd clapping their hands from a very far space. change is coming from all directions towards some strange unpredictable path. on a cycle of birth and death, destruction and creation. -my pet rock, orange || ooakosimo
